headline.main: Vonn Places 2nd in World Cup Downhill at 2018 Olympic Site
headline.print_headline: Vonn Places 2nd in World Cup Downhill at 2018 Olympic Site

lead_paragraph: Lindsey Vonn went first out of the gate in Saturday's World Cup downhill race and it nearly paid off.
